# Frontier Handoff Skill

Write:

- `handoffs/<CAMPAIGN_ID>/<PHASE_ID>.md`

Must include:

- branch
- commits
- files changed
- scope completed
- validation run
- non-runs and why
- risks or caveats
- review request focus
- next recommended step
